hopobject.body: Could you send me an application form? montclair pharmacy It surveyed patients attending eight NHS trusts and two independent sector treatment centres and found that half did not remember being given a choice of hospital and of those that did, just 5% had looked at quality information on NHS Choices or other websites. Most patients drew on their own experience, GP advice and family and friends when deciding where to be treated.
